  "body": "Follow up of: https://github.com/status-im/status-mobile/pull/17414\r\n\r\nPR Design review comment: https://www.figma.com/file/Tf5nfkYvpbnNCo4rKLK7lS?node-id=6338:50422&mode=design#574331446\r\n\r\n## Problem\r\nIn the Messages/Author component, sometimes an extra space appears after the nickname gets truncated.\r\n\r\n![image](https://github.com/status-im/status-mobile/assets/19279756/255eb0f7-96f5-4052-8b19-9e6f1fb5cddf)\r\n\r\nWhile utilizing React Native TextView with the `number-of-lines` property set to `1`, an issue arises sporadically where the text container doesn't terminate immediately after the three dots ('...'). Instead, it occupies additional space, leading to unwanted blank space in the UI.\r\n\r\n",
